<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-03-0430 </DOCNO><TEXT>These Research Centers were established to undertake large-scale researchin pure science and long-term technologically orientated research. Theyare also now concerned with environmental studies in connection withnuclear power. The initial focus in the safe-handling of radiation andradioactive material has broadened to cover a wider area of environmentalresearch, including radiation and radionuclides, environmental chemicals,wastes (chemical and radioactive), water and soil, the atmosphere, climateand systems analysis (mainly related to risk assessment). Each is discussedin turn and the research outlined.</TEXT></DOC>